{"type": "article", "id": 8612, "title": "买之前，法拉利允许你用 iPad 应用把车大卸八块", "description": "有了这款应用，不买（买不起）法拉利的人兴许也会想去展厅折腾一下。", "date": "2015-04-17T08:38:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1928, "name": "AR"}, {"id": 3862, "name": "法拉利"}, {"id": 2601, "name": "宝马"}, {"id": 8415, "name": "捷豹路虎"}, {"id": 9048, "name": "ZSpace"}, {"id": 9049, "name": "Metaio"}], "category": 4, "column": null, "author": 43366, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604223558SIqhX8V37cop6NQK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t最近各大汽车厂商对 AR 技术相当热衷，<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/8360.html\" target=\"_blank\">宝马要在上海车展上发布一款 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">AR </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">眼镜</span></a>，捷豹路虎要做<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/7864.html\" target=\"_blank\">“智能挡风玻璃”</a>。而法拉利则想把 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">AR </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">技术用在更加现实点的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">iPad </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应用上。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t这款名为<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/14/8409583/ferrari-augmented-reality-app-metaio\" target=\"_blank\"> <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Ferrari AR Showroom </span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/14/8409583/ferrari-augmented-reality-app-metaio\" target=\"_blank\">的应用</a>目前还只在日本和澳大利亚上线，美国版预期在 5 月 20 日举行的</span> <a href=\"http://www.insidear2015.com/san-francisco/\" target=\"_blank\">InsideAR 展</a>上发布，包括中国在内的其它地区<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">则尚未确定</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">不过 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DT5Wd8mvAgE\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DT5Wd8mvAgE\" target=\"_blank\">上的一段视频</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">展示了它相当酷炫的使用场景：用 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">iPad </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">打开 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">AR Showroom </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应用，摄像头对准展厅里的一辆法拉利跑车，扫描之后，你就能对这辆法拉利“动手手脚”，比如让车换个颜色试试效果或者看看发动机的内部结构等等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我们把视频搬运了一下：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"510\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XOTM1NTE0OTgw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t这款应用是法拉利和软件应用开发商 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.zspace.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">ZSPACE</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">合作的产品，运用了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Metaio </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://blog.metaio.com/2014/11/06/hybrid-tracking-metaio-6-takes-3d-object-tracking-to-new-heights/\" target=\"_blank\">3D </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://blog.metaio.com/2014/11/06/hybrid-tracking-metaio-6-takes-3d-object-tracking-to-new-heights/\" target=\"_blank\">物体追踪技术</a>。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">大致就是探测物体的边缘和形状，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">3D </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">建模之后自动判断其是否是特定型号的法拉利。这项</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">技术目前已经相当成熟，今年 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">VentureBeat </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">就曾<a href=\"http://venturebeat.com/2015/01/19/microsoft-researchs-autocharge-can-automatically-charge-smartphones-with-light-beams/\" target=\"_blank\">报道</a>微软研究院正在用它来研发自动追踪桌面上的手机然后<a href=\"http://venturebeat.com/2015/01/19/microsoft-researchs-autocharge-can-automatically-charge-smartphones-with-light-beams/\" target=\"_blank\">自动充电</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的技术。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t探测出眼前法拉利车的“真身”之后，这款 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">AR Showroom </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">应用还能结合内置的数据，显示这辆车的内部结构，这就像是给车做一次 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">X </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">光检测。要是拖动屏幕，用户还能看到车内部每个零件的分解图，如果对目前的状况不满意，还可以换点零件装上去试试。此外，这款应用有模拟风洞功能，可以测试跑车在一定风速下的运动状况。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">总之它能让你在买车前把眼前法拉利车的里里外外都折腾一遍，彻底了解之后再买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t不过目前这款应用还只能用于法拉利的 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">款特定车型（<span style=\"color:#444444;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16.5px;line-height:31.1666660308838px;\">458 Speciale、Spider、FF、California 以及 F12berlinetta</span>），当然其它车型的适配相信也不会花太久。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t事实上，据 <a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/9/8379939/mini-augmented-vision-ar-augmented-reality\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">The Verge </span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/9/8379939/mini-augmented-vision-ar-augmented-reality\" target=\"_blank\">报道</a>，宝马 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">MINI </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">即将发布的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">AR </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">眼镜除了能帮你在车里导航之外，也具备在车外透视宝马 MINI 的功能，只是宝马用了什么技术目前还不清楚。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">题图来源：<a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/104990235036869005/\" target=\"_blank\">Pinterest</a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}